2026-05-16T07:14:21.5568030Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T07:14:21.5568931Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T07:14:21.5569789Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
